title: Kubera - One Last God
description:
Gods with everlasting lives. Sura who possess unrivaled power. And humans, caught helplessly in-between. When Kubera's peaceful village meets its fiery end, a mysterious magician named Asha comes to her rescue. Together they begin a journey in search of answers and revenge. Meanwhile across the realms, a web of entwined fates is growing tighter. One by one the other players of the game will emerge, each with their own agenda to pursue. At the center of this maelstrom stands Kubera, the girl with a god's name. Will this sixteen-year-old be the salvation of the world or its destruction?

There is a scanlation gap due to official translation being acceptable during s3-8 until s3-160. Make sure to comeback since translation suffers afterwards and side stories were never officially translated. You can find the official [here](https://www.webtoons.com/en/fantasy/kubera/list?title%5Fno=83)
